						               													<description>Mighty fights, max fun!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In Super Power 8, the players fight with each other in 5 fierce battles. Each battle, reveal as many score cards from the deck as the number of players. Every player simultaneously plays a fighter card from their hand face-down then reveals them.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;If two or more players play the same fighter, they discard them. The remaining players resolve their fighter ability in ascending order (1-8), and then choose a score card in descending order (8-1). Those with fighters discarded draw one random score card. All played and discarded cards are placed face-up in front of the owner for the rest of the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;After 5 battles, each player totals their points from &amp;#10;&amp;#10;     Values of score cards&amp;#10;     Fighter #3 (if successfully played)&amp;#10;     Bonus for having a certain combination of card colors (similar to poker hands)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The player with the highest points wins! In case of a tie, play another round and the player who plays the highest card (after resolving fighter abilities) is the winner.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
